u%20enter%20the%20office%2C%20there's%20a%20giant%20yellow%20sun%20logo%20hanging%20from%20the%20ceiling.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20Walmart%20logo%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20said%2C%20pointing%20up%20at%20it.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Walmart's%20old%20e-commerce%20office%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20bother%20to%20take%20the%20sign%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20another%20flashback.%20I'd%20been%20here%20before%20as%20part%20of%20my%20quest%20to%20refashion%20myself%20into%20a%20tech%20writer.%20Over%20a%20decade%20earlier%20I'd%20walked%20this%20same%20floor%20with%20Venky%20Harinarayan%20and%20Anand%20Rajaraman%2C%20another%20pair%20of%20tech%20entrepreneurs%2C%20who%20ran%20Walmart's%20e-commerce%20incubator%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mill's%20Silicon%20Valley%20office%20(with%20an%20old%20Walmart%20logo%20on%20the%20ceiling)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917f88689026fbb4d0dbcb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMill's%20Silicon%20Valley%20office%20(with%20an%20old%20Walmart%20logo%20on%20the%20ceiling)%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242463855-4fda-477b-af98-ffede46aa28e%5C%22%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bstink%20bomb%26quot%3B%20area%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20present%20day%2C%20Matt%20took%20me%20on%20a%20tour%20and%20introduced%20me%20to%20Adam%20Mittleman%2C%20Mill's%20head%20of%20engineering%20(another%20former%20Apple%20designer).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20testing%20areas%20where%20the%20devices%20are%20opened%2C%20closed%2C%20rotated%2C%20heated%2C%20shaken%2C%20and%20dropped%20to%20ensure%20they%20last%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20the%20%26quot%3Bstink%20bomb%26quot%3B%20area%2C%20where%20chemical%20engineers%20work%20on%20new%20ways%20to%20keep%20your%20food%20scraps%20smelling%20fragrant%2C%20not%20foul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20showed%20me%20a%20tub%20of%20old%20food%20and%20pointed%20to%20a%20giant%20bin%20of%20the%20finished%20product%3A%20light%20brown%20%26quot%3Bfood%20grounds%26quot%3B%20that%20are%2080%25%20lighter%20and%20completely%20dry.%20This%20can%20be%20stored%20for%20months%20and%20put%20on%20gardens%20and%20other%20areas%20to%20fertilize%20plants.%20Or%20Mill%20can%20pick%20it%20up%20for%20you%2C%20for%20a%20fee%2C%20and%20put%20it%20to%20use%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Material%20created%20by%20the%20Mill%20Food%20Recycler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917f921abd5e944effad1ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaterial%20created%20by%20the%20Mill%20Food%20Recycler%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20is%20transforming%20wet%2C%20sticky%20old%20food%20into%20much%20lighter%20material%20that%20doesn't%20go%20off.%20The%20sleek%20Mill%20device%20can%20turn%20100%20pounds%20of%20food%20waste%20into%20roughly%2020%20pounds%20of%20dry%20%26quot%3Bgrounds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22744c22fb-5c22-4a61-96b8-4aef5c8d2ab5%5C%22%3EMaking%20food%20scraps%20lighter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20does%20this%20matter%3F%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20collecting%20and%20processing%20garbage%20is%20related%20to%20food%20waste.%20It's%20heavy%20and%20goes%20off%20so%20quickly%20that%20garbage%20trucks%20must%20run%20collection%20routes%20regularly%2C%20and%20they%20burn%20more%20diesel%20carrying%20that%20extra%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Mill%20can%20turn%20everyone's%20food%20scraps%20into%20much%20lighter%2C%20storable%20material%2C%20then%20garbage%20collection%20can%20happen%20less%20frequently%20and%20use%20less%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMill%20Food%20Recyclers%20are%20currently%20in%20tens%20of