%2C%20had%20their%20own%20jargon%20and%20complicated%20strategy%20systems%2C%20even%20if%20the%20advice%20largely%20boiled%20down%20to%20%26quot%3BBe%20confident%2C%20and%20go%20talk%20to%20girls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Ackman%2C%20a%20hedge-fund%20manager%20and%20highly%20active%20social-media%20poster%2C%20recently%20sparked%20a%20minor%20meme%20cycle.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20youth%2C%20Ackman%20tweeted%20what%20he%20said%20was%20his%20old%20go-to%20line%20for%20initiating%20conversation%20with%20a%20woman%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-may-i-meet-you-advice-talking-to-women-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMay%20I%20meet%20you%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20hear%20from%20many%20young%20men%20that%20they%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20meet%20young%20women%20in%20a%20public%20setting.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20online%20culture%20has%20destroyed%20the%20ability%20to%20spontaneously%20meet%20strangers.%20As%20such%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20share%20a%20few%20words%20that%20I%20used%20in%20my%20youth%20to%20meet%20someone%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bill%20Ackman%20(%40BillAckman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1989793183698714946%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20online%20reaction%20to%20his%20advice%20has%20been%2C%20um%2C%20skeptical.%20Some%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20slightly%20weird%20line%20would%20work%20only%20if%20you%20were%20already%20tall%2C%20rich%2C%20and%20good-looking%2C%20and%20could%20come%20off%20creepy%20to%20most%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20were%20more%20positive%2C%20saying%20the%20line%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20jumping-off%20point%20for%20a%20more%20sincere%20conversation.%20Grindr's%20sex%20and%20relationship%20expert%2C%20Zachary%20Zane%2C%20said%20he%20thinks%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsolid%20icebreaker.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20someone%20the%20opportunity%2Fautonomy%20to%20cut%20to%20the%20chase%20and%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20talk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20my%20colleague%20Sydney%20Bradley.%20At%20least%20one%20person%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpenguin_pmkt%2Fstatus%2F1990177465160134995%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20claimed%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethey%20tried%20out%20the%20line%20and%20it%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20frankly%20don't%20think%2C%20'May%20I%20meet%20you%3F'%20is%20going%20to%20cut%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Myles%20Slayton%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20dating%20app%20Cerca.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20thesis%20of%20what%20he's%20saying%20is%20true.%20Men%20are%20not%20approaching%20women%20as%20much%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20has%20hit%20on%20something%20real%3A%20It's%20always%20been%20intimidating%20to%20shoot%20your%20shot%20with%20someone%2C%20but%20for%20Gen%20Z%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20age%20of%20dating%20apps%20and%20social%20media%2C%20it%20may%20be%20even%20more%20uncomfortable%20to%20strike%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20an%20appealing%20stranger.%20Young%20single%20people%20long%20to%20meet%20someone%20in%20person%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20this%20is%20how%20you%20do%20it.%20Sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20be%20the%20mildly%20awkward%20person%20who%20says%20a%20weird%20line.%20At%20worst%2C%20you%20get%20turned%20down!%20Be%20bold!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20based%20on%20my%20nearly%2010%2C000%20hours%20of%20PUA%20knowledge%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BMay%20I%20meet%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20is%2C%20indeed%2C%20not%20the%20best%20line%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bcold%20approach.%26quot%3B%20The%20successful%20kinds%20of%20opening%20lines%20that%20true%20pickup%20artists%20suggest%20are%20more%20specific%20and%20better%20at%20leading%20to%20a%20conversation.%20A%20line%20that%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20always%20loved%20from%20the%202007%20VH1%20show%20with%20Mystery%20was%20to%20ask%20someone%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20did%20you%20just%20see%20the%20fight%20outside%3F%26quot%3B%20(There%20would%20be%2C%20of%20course%2C%20no%20fight%2C%20but%20it%20would%20start%20a%20conversation.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tactic%20would%20be%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHelp%20my%20friend%20and%20me%20settle%20an%20argument%3A%20%3Cem%3EChoose%20your%20own%20lightweight%20but%20debatable%20topic%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20this%20works%20well%20for%20approaching%20a%20group%20of%20people%2C%20not%20just%20a%20single%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20these%20tactics%20work%20because%20they%20allow%20you%20to%20strike%20up%20a%20conversation%20without%20seeming%20like%20you're%20a%20sad%2C%20thirsty%20guy%20trying%20to%20hit%20on%20a%20stranger.%20Get%20the%20conversation%20flowing%20first%2C%20then%20you%20can%20start%20laying%20on%20the%20charm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Ackman's%20line%20is%20lacking.%20It's%20too%20obvious%20about%20your%20intentions%20to%20hit%20on%20the%20person.%20Plus%2C%20what%20comes%20next%3F%20You%20ask%20her%20name%3F%20How%20boring!%20Yuck!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20biggest%20hurdle%20the%20PUAs%20help%20coach%20young%20men%20through%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Binner%20game.%26quot%3B%20The%20thing%20that's%20holding%20men%20back%20from%20approaching%20women%20and%20striking%20up%20a%20conversation%20isn't%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20right%20magic%20incantation%20or%20phrase%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20lack%20of%20confidence%20or%20shyness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20awkward%20approaching%20a%20stranger%20to%20talk%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20getting%20over%20that%20fear%20and%20awkwardness%20is%20the%20hardest%20part.%20Some%20PUAs%20recommend%20lower-stakes%20practice%2C%20such%20as%20talking%20to%20old%20ladies%20in%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20just%20to%20build%20confidence%20about%20approaching%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20using%20Ackman's%20line%20gives%20someone%20the%20confidence%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20stranger%20(politely!)%20in%20a%20bar%2C%20then%20they're%20already%2075%25%20of%20the%20way%20there.%20The%20hardest%20part%20is%20just%20saying%20%3Cem%3Eanything%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20who%20cares%20what%20the%20corny%20line%20is!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20browsing%20through%20Reddit's%20r%2Fseduction%20forum%20today%20to%20see%20if%20they%20had%20caught%20wind%20of%20Ackman's%20suggestion%20(they%20hadn't).%20But%20instead%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20interesting%20recent%20post%20that%20suggested%20a%20new%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fseduction%2Fcomments%2F1op6v04%2Fstupid_simple_natural_seduction_method_that_no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estupid%20simple%20natural%20seduction%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20meeting%20women%2C%20and%20detailed%20a%204-step%20plan%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E1)%20Get%20good%20at%20an%20interest%20or%20hobby%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E2)%20Organize%20events%20around%20it%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E3)%20Be%20seen%20as%20the%20leader%20by%20girls%20who%20attend%20those%20events%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E4)%20Choose%20the%20girls%20you%20like%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20being%20a%20well-rounded%2C%20normal%20person%20with%20interests%20may%20help%20more%20than%20a%20snazzy%20opening%20line.%20Even%20the%20professional%20PUAs%20agree!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAdditional%20reporting%20by%20Sydney%20Bradley.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%