3Cli%3EMoney%20has%20been%20allocated%20for%20construction%20related%20to%20the%20B-21%20Raider%20bomber%20and%20Sentinel%20ICBM.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENuclear%20modernization%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20but%20some%20cost%20overruns%20and%20delays%20have%20affected%20these%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20just%20got%20a%20burst%20of%20extra%20funding%20for%20its%20new%20strategic%20bomber%20and%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20programs%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20tucked%20into%20last%20week's%20government%20shutdown%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20will%20go%20to%20construction%20projects%20supporting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-b21-bomber-designed-to-use-weapons-not-invented-yet-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EB-21%20Raider%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-extend-50-year-old-icbms-new-delayed-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESentinel%20ICBM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20high%20priorities%20for%20the%20Air%20Force%20amid%20efforts%20to%20modernize%20its%20platforms%20capable%20of%20delivering%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESigned%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20last%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20spending%20package%20provides%20the%20Air%20Force%20with%20%243.9%20billion%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.appropriations.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fmcva_divdjes.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20construction%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20above%20the%20service's%20budget%20request%20for%20fiscal%20year%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%20%24850%20million%20is%20designated%20for%20infrastructure%20supporting%20the%20B-21%20and%20Sentinel.%20Air%20Force%20bases%20like%20Ellsworth%2C%20Whiteman%2C%20and%20Dyess%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20house%20the%20B-21%20for%20training%20and%20main%20operations