cost%20overruns%20and%20delivery%20delays%2C%20which%20the%20Pentagon%20has%20blamed%20on%20an%20unrealistic%20delivery%20schedule%2C%20problems%20with%20Sentinel's%20engineering%20and%20system%20design%2C%20an%20atrophied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-will-launch-an-unarmed-minuteman-iii-icbm-across-the-pacific-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EICBM%20industrial%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20organizational%20issues%20within%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20watchdog%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20Force%20officials%20have%20said%20much%20of%20the%20Sentinel's%20cost%20growth%20has%20gone%20toward%20modernizing%20infrastructure%20for%20launch%20facilities%20and%20constructing%20new%20silos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20%24850%20million%20going%20toward%20the%20B-21%20and%20Sentinel%20programs%20is%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20bucket%20for%20two%20very%20costly%20projects.%20The%20B-21%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20lifetime%20cost%20of%20%24200%20billion%2C%20while%20the%20cost%20for%20Sentinel%20has%20ballooned%20to%20over%20%24140%20billion%2C%20but%20it%20is%20fairly%20substantial%20at%20the%20base%20level%20as%20an%20infrastructure%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20money%20for%20both%20Sentinel%20and%20B-21%20infrastructure%20comes%20as%20Air%20Force%20officials%20continue%20to%20emphasize%20nuclear%20modernization%2C%20as%20the%20service%20operates%20two%20legs%20of%20the%20US%20nuclear%20triad.%20The%20US%20Navy's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustry-knows-how-to-build-warships-navy-shipbuilding-insider-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EColumbia-class%20ballistic%20missile%20submarine%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Navy's%20own%20major%20modernization%20effort%2C%20is%20also%20under%20construction%20as%20an%20upgrade%20to%20submarine-based%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20though%20it%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20delays%2